{"tid":1855781,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[陰謀論]武漢P4實驗室","createTime":"2020-02-01T09:11:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-01T09:14:44.000Z","uid":347492,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6d17c56d18e3794a822af5930be64551ef33ae01","tid":1855781,"uid":347492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T09:11:01.000Z","msg":"最近好似有印度佬研究話2019-nCoV係SARS再加d HIV特徵而個3D structure又好神奇地fit到我地細胞嘅receptor binding site<br />\nSources: <a href=\"https://www.biorxiv.org/content/10.1101/2020.01.30.927871v1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.biorxiv.org%2Fcontent%2F10.1101%2F2020.01.30.927871v1&d=HQiZr%2BzFLDuBt%2FA%2FXRO5IkYnXQRGGZgEWtwyrMN1cgk%3D&h=6895c58e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.biorxiv.org/content/10.1101/2020.01.30.927871v1</a><br />\n再加上武漢果邊d病徵好散(e.g.有啲冇發燒,有啲腹瀉,個潛伏期又由1日到14日都有) <br />\n有&ldquo;謠言&rdquo;話武漢果邊唔止流行緊2019-nCoV,仲流行緊SARS,因為SARS潛伏期較短,而且病人會有腹瀉徵狀<br />\n眾所周知,武漢P4實驗室有研究開SARS,亦有將病毒注入動物測試既習慣<br />\n所以我就諗會唔會係P4實驗室d人研究完SARS,加啲HIV特徵整左2019-nCoV之後,冇好好將實驗動物(e.g.猴子)銷毀,跟住比啲無良商人執左去華南海鮮市場到賣,最後大爆發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(利申:小弟非微生物學專業,以上純屬個人ff,希望唔係真）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b97f793dd02d34280f901df7eafc553bc4a07e30","tid":1855781,"uid":188685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T09:14:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">02.03 同醫護一齊大罷工<br />\n支持醫護罷工</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mpfmKnS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmpfmKnS.jpg&h=a11077bd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gK3O8Py.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgK3O8Py.jpg&h=7a84bfe5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NVaByhV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNVaByhV.png&h=481301fd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8fY3XHU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8fY3XHU.jpg&h=a1323c58&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rA6MVuA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrA6MVuA.jpg&h=3365fef4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GrVRm9B.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGrVRm9B.png&h=e8588fe8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9dRhhHX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9dRhhHX.png&h=f80709fc&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}